---
title: Cal Smart Breaded Turkey with Potatoes, Broccoli and Honey-Dijon
description: Tonight, golden breaded turkey gets a low-cal makeover with Dijon mustard in place of egg or mayo. Roasted potatoes and broccoli make for simple and filling sides for a feel-good meal that's full of flavour!

